{"arkId":"cl010113228","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113228","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Cabinet","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Cabinet"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Deuxi\u00e8me R\u00e9publique (1848-1852) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1848","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 564 - Duc de Nemours","room":"Salle 564, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1848,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"Milieu du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Klagmann, Jean Baptiste Jules","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1810","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1867","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Sculpteur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q2415052"},{"label":"Fragonard, Alexandre-\u00c9variste","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1850","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1780","place":"Grasse","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"Peintre sur c\u00e9ramique","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q704938"},{"label":"Manufacture de S\u00e8vres","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q653307"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 12135","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"mobilier ; cabinet","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Cabinet orn\u00e9 de plaques de porcelaine et de figures en biscuit repr\u00e9sentant des all\u00e9gories. Les encadrements sont en \u00e9mail peint.\r\nCe coffret ou armoire \u00e0 bijoux t\u00e9moigne de la vitalit\u00e9 des recherches men\u00e9es \u00e0 S\u00e8vres sous la Seconde R\u00e9publique, sous la direction de Jacques-Joseph Ebelmen et sous la tutelle du Conseil de perfectionnement des manufactures. Sa confection r\u00e9unit de nombreux collaborateurs. L\u2019ornemaniste Jules Peyre donne le dessin g\u00e9n\u00e9ral, de style n\u00e9o-Renaissance, qui est corrig\u00e9 par Jules Di\u00e9terle, \u00ab artiste en chef \u00bb depuis 1848. L\u2019\u00e9b\u00e9nisterie est assum\u00e9e par Nikel, et par Jules Fossey pour les parties sculpt\u00e9es ; les plaques rondes, repr\u00e9sentant la Po\u00e9sie et la Musique, sont peintes par Alexandre-Evariste Fragonard d\u2019apr\u00e8s les m\u00e9daillons cr\u00e9\u00e9s par Rapha\u00ebl pour la vo\u00fbte de la Chambre de la Signature au Vatican ; les figures en biscuit sont r\u00e9alis\u00e9es d\u2019apr\u00e8s les mod\u00e8les de Klagmann ; les bronzes sont d\u2019Armand Feuch\u00e8re ; enfin l\u2019\u00e9mail peint tient une place important dans l\u2019ornementation de ce coffret : les plaques, \u00e0 d\u00e9cor d\u2019entrelacs et de rosaces, sont l\u2019\u0153uvre de Meyer Heine, qui dirige le tout jeune atelier d\u2019\u00e9maillage cr\u00e9\u00e9 \u00e0 S\u00e8vres en 1845. \r\nLe coffret est pr\u00e9sent\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019exposition des manufactures en 1850. En d\u00e9cembre 1851, le Prince-Pr\u00e9sident Napol\u00e9on-Bonaparte l\u2019offre \u00e0 la reine Isabelle II, sans doute \u00e0 l\u2019occasion de la naissance de sa fille Isabelle.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Profondeur","value":"45","displayDimension":"45 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"83","displayDimension":"83 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"87","displayDimension":"87 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Eb\u00e8ne, porcelaine, \u00e9mail peint, bronze dor\u00e9\r\nMat\u00e9riau : \u00e9b\u00e8ne\r\nMat\u00e9riau : porcelaine\r\nTechnique : \u00e9mail peint (techniques m\u00e9tal-\u003E\u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : bronze (dor\u00e9)","placeOfCreation":"S\u00e8vres (Ile-de-France = Ile de France-\u003EHauts-de-Seine = Hauts de Seine)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Expos\u00e9 par la manufacture de S\u00e8vres en 1850 ; offert en d\u00e9cembre 1851 par le Prince-Pr\u00e9sident Louis-Napol\u00e9on Bonaparte \u00e0 la reine d\u0027Espagne Isabelle II (1830-1904) ; collection Marie-Christine de Habsbourg, reine d\u0027Espagne (1858-1929) ; vente, Madrid, Finarte, 21 octobre 1999 ; collection Roberto Polo ; collection Jacques Vuill\u00e8me ; cabinet Blondeau-Br\u00e9ton-Prad\u00e8re ; don Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 des Amis du Louvre, 2004.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 des Amis du Louvre","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don manuel","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"11\/03\/2004","startYear":2004,"endYear":2004},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"17\/03\/2004","startYear":2004,"endYear":2004},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"25\/03\/2004","startYear":2004,"endYear":2004}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don manuel"}],"period":[{"value":"Deuxi\u00e8me R\u00e9publique (1848-1852)"}],"place":[{"value":"S\u00e8vres"}],"objectType":[{"value":"mobilier"},{"value":"cabinet"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 des Amis du Louvre. 2000-2010. Dix ans d\u0027acquisitions, Paris, Editions du mus\u00e9e du Louvre (Grande Galerie, le journal du Louvre); TTM \u00e9ditions, 2010","bibliographyDate":"2010","bibliographyDetail":"p. 47;49, p. 47","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000113228\/0000240311_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000113228\/0000240311_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2004 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean-Gilles Berizzi","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000113228\/0000240314_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000113228\/0000240314_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2004 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean-Gilles Berizzi","type":"","position":1},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000113228\/0000240315_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000113228\/0000240315_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2004 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean-Gilles Berizzi","type":"","position":2},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000113228\/0000240316_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000113228\/0000240316_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2004 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean-Gilles Berizzi","type":"","position":3},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000113228\/0000240317_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000113228\/0000240317_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2004 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e